@startuml error_recovery
title Error & Recovery: Failed Write During Sync

participant "Software Architect" as architect
participant "Core" as bausteinsicht_cli_core
participant "Engine" as bausteinsicht_sync_engine
participant "Document" as bausteinsicht_drawio_document
participant "State" as bausteinsicht_sync_state

architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_core : 1. bausteinsicht sync
bausteinsicht_cli_core -> bausteinsicht_sync_engine : 2. Run(...) — pure, in-memory
bausteinsicht_sync_engine --> bausteinsicht_cli_core : 3. SyncResult
bausteinsicht_cli_core -> bausteinsicht_drawio_document : 4. SaveDocument(arch.drawio) — atomic temp-file + rename
bausteinsicht_cli_core -> bausteinsicht_sync_state : 5. if write succeeded: SaveState(.bausteinsicht-sync), SHA-256 checksummed
bausteinsicht_cli_core --> architect : 6. if write failed: exit 1, original files intact, state unchanged
bausteinsicht_cli_core --> architect : 7. if write succeeded: summary
architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_core : 8. next run: bausteinsicht sync
bausteinsicht_cli_core -> bausteinsicht_cli_core : 9. state unchanged from failed run → DetectChanges re-finds same delta
bausteinsicht_cli_core --> architect : 10. completes the interrupted change, no manual repair

@enduml
